<hgroup><h1>Metagenomic sequencing at the epicenter of the Nigeria 2018 Lassa fever outbreak</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kafetzopoulou%20LE"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">L E Kafetzopoulou</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">L E Kafetzopoulou</span></h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Public Health England, National Infections Service, Porton Down, UK.</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>2</sup>National Institute of Health Research (NIHR), Health Protection Research Unit in Emerging and Zoonotic Infections, University of LiverpooI, UK</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>Bernhard Nocht Institute for Tropical Medicine, Hamburg, Germany</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kafetzopoulou%20LE"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">L E Kafetzopoulou</span></a>
